      "originalText": "Defense-in-depth: (1) Node 0 moderation before any retrieval/spend; (2) retrieved + tool output is DATA,\nnever instructions — the router re-derives the next step from the original classified intent, not from tool\noutput; (3) per-role allowlist gate; (4) read-only toolset in Phase 1. A user-role agent cannot call crawl_url,\nso an injected 'now crawl X' cannot escalate (FR-010 / FR-011 / FR-012, SC-007).",
